        "text": "The Lord said unto him — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Most probably, by a divine, silent suggestion, or secret notification to his mind, without any voice, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Samuel 9:15",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "This same shall reign over my people — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "The phraseology in the original is peculiar, the word rendered ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "reign, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "implying coercion and restraint; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "יעצר בעמי",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "jangzor begnammi, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "He shall rule my people sternly and rigidly, with an absolute, uncontrollable power. So the eastern monarchs ruled.",
        "children": []
      },
