        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "When Samuel saw Saul, the Lord answered him, sc., in reply to the tacit inquiry, 'Is this he?' \"Behold, this is the man of whom I spake to thee.\" עצר, coercere imperio. ",
        "children": []
      }
